{"tid":1716352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(急)所有荃灣手足入黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:08:19.000Z","uid":156681,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"174676e50e82aad170ca46f701bef9eb366e2158","tid":1716352,"uid":156681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:21:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚出黎嘅手足<br />\n應該都知企咗成晚大鴻輝<br />\nSet晒rb玩埋魔法<br />\n班曱甴都完全當我地冇到<br />\n得廿幾隻企喺荃新門口唔知做乜鳩<br />\n我地出黎目的係幫暴大手足分散曱甴火力<br />\n但琴晚喺大鴻輝幾個鐘完全做唔撚到呀<br />\n白白浪費咗幾個鐘呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直到推上葵桶邨班曱甴先開始做野</span></span><br />\n呢個先係我地想要嘅效果呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為嗰度有棟狗宿舍</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗宿舍係狗春袋</span></span><br />\n麻煩咁多位手足今晚瞄準春袋<br />\n做啲真正幫到成個運動嘅野<br />\n行動要升級<br />\n分散對家火力<br />\n學吓天水圍手足<br />\n應承我得唔撚得？"},{"pid":"20910a615fc89c00dcb29a79af782d1ef9c082b5","tid":1716352,"uid":156681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔撚郁"},{"pid":"26dda3059c908679028e5b41b015e720e5ae8ff7","tid":1716352,"uid":26774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"認真召喚火魔法師上葵涌村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先下手為強"},{"pid":"1cecc6c2ca7d553e5f1020c1ab40cd3f70d0a47b","tid":1716352,"uid":156681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"狗宿舍再推仲有葵涌狗屋<br />\nHit and run"},{"pid":"dbb60eed27962cb929d0e129fb5dfda458c2b2ee","tid":1716352,"uid":311796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"今日開花直接係葵涌邨？"},{"pid":"087c2ff6f61b0c45219f0e2daf9d686b0ef757ee","tid":1716352,"uid":212410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc23cee7918fe3a