駕車途經事發現場，目睹該男子從高處墮下，當場折斷雙手並失去知覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60264041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60264041&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=2801d3b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60264041&h=b809e4bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60264041</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師我屌曬你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}